#. Tag: guisubmenu
#: index.docbook:468
#, no-c-format
msgid "Layout"
msgstr "Raspored"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:469
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This allows to choose between various &graphviz; layout algorithms or to "
"choose your own one. The entries, as described on the &graphviz; homepage, "
"are the following:"
msgstr ""
"Ovo omogućava da biraju između različitih  &graphviz; algoritama rasporeda "
"ili da izabere svoj vlastiti. Unosi , kao što je opisano na &graphviz; "
"stranici , su sljedeći :"

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:473
#, no-c-format
msgid "&dot;"
msgstr "&dot;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:474
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&dot; algorithm, default for directed graphs. It produces "
"<quote>hierarchical</quote> or layered drawings of directed graphs. The "
"layout algorithm lays edges in the same direction (top to bottom, or left to "
"right), and then attempts to avoid edge crossings and to reduce edge length."
msgstr ""
"&dot; algoritam, podrazumijevano za usmjerene grafove . Proizvodi <quote> "
"hijerarhijske </quote> ili u slojevima crteža usmjerene grafove. "
"Raspoređivački algoritam postavlja ivice u istom smjeru (od vrha do dna , "
"ili s lijeva na desno ) , a zatim pokušava da izbjegne ukrštanja rubova i da "
"smanji dužine rubova ."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:478
#, no-c-format
msgid "&neato;"
msgstr "&neato;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:479
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&neato; algorithm, default for undirected graphs. It produces <quote>spring "
"model</quote> layouts. It uses the Kamada-Kawai algorithm, which is "
"equivalent to statistical multi-dimensional scaling."
msgstr ""
"&neato; algoritam, podrazumijevani za neusmjerene grafove. Proizvodi <quote> "
"model opruge</quote> raspored . On koristi algoritam Kamada - Kawai , što je "
"ekvivalentno statističkom multidimenzionalnom skaliranju."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:483
#, no-c-format
msgid "&twopi;"
msgstr "&twopi;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:484
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&twopi; algorithm, for directed and undirected graphs. Radial layout, after "
"Graham Wills 1997."
msgstr ""
"&twopi; algoritam, za usmjerene i neusmjerene grafove. Radijalni raspored, "
"prema Graham Wills 1997. godine."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:488
#, no-c-format
msgid "&fdp;"
msgstr "&fdp;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:489
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&fdp; algorithm, for undirected graphs. It produces <quote>spring model</"
"quote> layouts. It implements the Fruchterman-Reingold heuristic including a "
"multigrid solver that handles larger graphs and clustered undirected graphs."
msgstr ""
"&fdp; algoritam , za neusmjerene grafove . Proizvodi <quote> model opruge  </"
"quote> rasporede . To implementira Fruchterman - Reingold heuristiku "
"uključujući višemrežni rješavač koji obrađuje veće grafikona i grupisane "
"neusmjerene grafikone."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:493
#, no-c-format
msgid "&circo;"
msgstr "&circo;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:494
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&circo; algorithm. It produces a circular layout, after Six and Tollis 1999, "
"Kauffman and Wiese 2002. Suitable for certain diagrams of multiple cyclic "
"structures."
msgstr ""
"&circo;  algoritam. To proizvodi kružni raspored, po Six and Tollis 1999, "
"Kauffman i Wiese 2002. Pogodno za određene sheme višestrukih cikličkih "
"struktura."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:498
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "Specify layout command"
msgid "Specify Layout Command…"
msgstr "Odredite komandu rasporeda"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:499
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Opens a dialog allowing you to specify a layout command executed by the "
"shell. This command should accept one parameter, the graph file name, and "
"write its layout on stdout in the xdot language. This way, you can give "
"specific options to one of the previous commands, or apply a filter "
"modifying your graph before running it through &dot;."
msgstr ""
"Otvara dijalog omogućava vam da odredite raspored komandi izvedenim ljuske . "
"Ova naredba treba da prihvati jedan parametar , ime grafikonu datoteke i "
"pisati svoje rasporeda na stdout u xdot jeziku . Na ovaj način , možete dati "
"određene opcije jednom od prethodnih naredbi , ili primijeniti filter "
"dopunama svoj ​​grafikon prije pokretanja kroz &dot;."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:503
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "Reset layout command to defaults"
msgid "Reset Layout Command to Default"
msgstr "Vrati raspored komandi podrazumjevano"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:504
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Determine the graph type (directed or not) and apply the default algorithm "
"to it, currently &dot; and &neato; respectively."
msgstr ""
"Odredite grafikonu tip (usmjereni ili ne) i primjenite podrazumijevani "
"algoritam za to , trenutno &dot; i &neato; respektivno ."

